											input(type="input" class="form-control" id="telefon" placeholder="telefon sau mobil")
									.col-xs-12.col-sm-6
										.form-group
											label(for="exampleInputEmail1")
												| Prof Mesajul dumnevoastra
											textarea(class="form-control" rows="8" placeholder="sau daca aveti alte observatii...")
									.col-xs-12
										.form-group
											label(for="projectPrez") Incarca fisier*
